NAME
	async_event - broadcast asynchronous event to subscribers

SYNOPSIS
	varargs void async_event(string name, mixed args...)


DESCRIPTION
	The function "evt_" + name is called asynchronously in all objects
	subscribed to this event, with as first argument the current object.
	Each call is done using the tick and stack resources of the subscribed
	object.

SEE ALSO
	efun/add_event, efun/event, efun/query_events, efun/remove_event
